<p style="font-size:0.85em;color:#888;font-style:italic;border-left:3px solid #e5e7eb;padding-left:10px;margin:8px 0 16px;">
  <strong>Medical Disclaimer:</strong> This article is general educational information for licensed clinicians and students, not medical advice or a substitute for your institution's protocols or a provider's orders. Always follow your facility's policies and a provider's orders.
